5b95709c550790700d94701e1e1b0604fd5ac0","tid":1501513,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7bc9ef437d320d16856fca58f905a3f7ac83689","tid":1501513,"uid":220305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:23:45.000Z","msg":"我今日原本發夢上左前線<br />\n後來有防暴包抄<br />\n啲人不停嗌走呀走呀<br />\n但其實嗰刻我唔想走住 唔想扔低前線既手足<br />\n我朋友後尾直接拉左我走<br />\n後來我地轉左場<br />\n同班狗對峙左一陣 <br />\n我朋友話同我地走先 因為啲防暴已經又開始包抄我地<br />\n我朋友驚我地女仔走唔切<br />\n所以話撤左先<br />\n後來上左車<br />\n見到沿路上有一班人一字排開 比成班防暴圍住<br />\n我就開始諗佢地比人捉返狗屋既話 會比班狗點對待<br />\n再見到tg話有手足比狗打傷射傷<br />\n我嗰刻真係好崩潰 好想同佢地講對唔住<br />\n一直以黎我都係前線<br />\n但因為前排女手足嗰單野<br />\n所以我驚<br />\n我早走我懦弱<br />\n我冇同大家一齊走<br />\n各位手足 我對你地唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次我會同你地一齊黎一齊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"要保護別人<br />\n要先保護自己"},{"pid":"19305eb5572c3fc4dfcfcef37b0862f4ab3a1991","tid":1501513,"uid":8948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c364daf4be1118e4e29b616cbaeb4601ea5f059","tid":1501513,"uid":220305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5081dc8904835e2fbb3b802d9703bc2e6ae87ce3","tid":1501513,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e31e38e0898b922d8371b197e65963fb878bab","tid":1501513,"uid":220305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"有睇哂咁多位既cm 我下次會量力以為"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋如果有女仔肯叫啲企係戰區玩手機既人走先，實在係對前線好大幫忙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:37:39.000Z","msg":"岩岩的確見到唔少 <br />\n我會幫手嗌佢地走先<br />\n有啲嗌完唔聽真係冇辦法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"由七月開戰術post到今個月，都仲係成堆人出黎玩手機，有事先走佬<br />\n屌咩，有事個陣全場成千人一齊走，個地鐵點食到咁多人<br />\n玩手機不如開多條戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d69c2fefb0f6b3519fbc3f35c8fff0d54d374d","tid":1501513,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"下次出黎再見 不被捕"},{"pid":"8daabc91d7442693548fb59ca113d6fe81c5938a","tid":1501513,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:43:02.000Z","msg":"你决走係要，<br />\n後排唔走，前線唔走，<br />\n時間拖長左，警增援好快"},{"pid":"4b0de752a9b33cebdf4d4b5236d4436d9dc297ec","tid":1501513,"uid":21783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"你已經做得好好架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2ce52b901c6815e19c7c0ac78887d7166578b0","tid":1501513,"uid":256067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"辛苦了 今日我連出都冇出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申前線 明天會更落力"},{"pid":"7b08405e74a49ce7da97194ab7c3153ffd65f4b6","tid":1501513,"uid":220305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2ce52b901c6815e19c7c0ac78887d7166578b0","tid":1501513,"uid":256067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"辛苦了 今日我連出都冇出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申前線 明天會更落力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"你都辛苦了"},{"pid":"6dbd735affc4bcb2093f586459dc933a3a4ff72d","tid":1501513,"uid":110548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"1/9 同我拆撚曬d燈柱佢！全部鋸斷佢！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501712</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0feb49715f44abe26b6d7bd09134f86e2b5e8405","tid":1501513,"uid":